998
00:36:15,600 --> 00:36:18,580
 S jedne strane je mučeništvo.

999
00:36:18,580 --> 00:36:21,780
 Znači, to je znak mučeništva,

1000
00:36:21,780 --> 00:36:24,480
 u ostalom i u kršanstvu je

1001
00:36:24,480 --> 00:36:25,820
 crvena boja

1002
00:36:25,820 --> 00:36:26,880
 znak mučenika.

1003
00:36:26,880 --> 00:36:29,080
 Kada je, ne znam,

1004
00:36:29,080 --> 00:36:30,220
 kada je Sveti Stjepan

1005
00:36:30,220 --> 00:36:31,500
 nosite crvenu štolu,

1006
00:36:31,500 --> 00:36:34,000
 crvenu misnicu i tako dalje.

1007
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:34,860
 Znači,

1008
00:36:34,860 --> 00:36:37,920
